_source.name: Emanuele
_source.personal_title: Your Italian travel profiler and your Roman guide!

detailedPassions.description: I think street foods like a form to taste the culture of the place. While you are eating you can meet the local people and observe the city. You feel part of the city.
Street Photography helps me to understand the way of living in a city. You create a sort of connection between you, people and the city, and the photo camera is the tool.
Painting is a way to tells a story, a way in which you can describe the history or a fairy tale. I love it because it brings you to another world, shows you a different point of view.
I am a father of wonderful boys!

I’m an actor and a Choreografer and I used to be a dancer, so theater is definitely a part of my life. Theater helped me in my sad moments and it gives me great joy either when I’m on stage performing or when I’m among the audience watching a show.
I have a little dog, her name is Sophia, she’s family to me. She gives me love with no limits :)
I so love to explore new places, new cities, learning something about the history, the traditions, the food.
Because sometimes it is pleasant to get away from the chaos of the city
Because dogs are the dearest friends you could wish for!
